@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@productId = replace-with-product-id
@reservationId = replace-with-reservation-id
@orderId = replace-with-order-id

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### Create product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "NIKE-AJ1-BRED-2026",
  "brand": "Nike",
  "model": "Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG",
  "name": "Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Bred",
  "colorway": "Black/Varsity Red/White",
  "description": "Limited sneaker drop for a high-demand Jordan release.",
  "priceCents": 89900,
  "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556906781-9a412961c28c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80",
  "releaseAt": "2026-07-15T16:00:00.000Z",
  "stockTotal": 5
}

### Reserve one pair
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "customerEmail": "buyer@example.com",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Checkout reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/checkout

### Cancel reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel

### Cleanup expired reservations
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/cleanup/expired

### List reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations

### List orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

### Get order
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}
